<div class="auto-deposit-thanks">
	<h1>
		<svg class="icon icon-confirmation">
			<use xlink:href="#icon-confirmation"/>
		</svg>
		Thanks!
	</h1>

	<p>Every month your balance will
		<br class="so">grow by ${{deposit-amount}}!

	{{#has-donation}}
		<br class="so">
		<br>(You’re also making a ${{donation-amount}} donation
		<br class="so">to Kiva <br class="mo">each month – thank you!)
	{{/has-donation}}
	</p>

	<svg class="icon icon-email">
		<use xlink:href="#icon-email"/>
	</svg>
	<p>You’ll get an email after each deposit
		<br class="smo">so you can make more loans.</p>

	<p><strong>Auto lending is the fastest
		<br class="so">way to lend your balance</strong>
		<br><a href="{kvurl page=settings action=credit#auto-lend}">Define your criteria</a>
	</p>
</div>